Universal Plotter Output Subroutine Call Interface

Program calls driver setup - driver returns:

	driver structure version - for upward compatible structure upgrades
	pointer to driver structure which contains:

		capabilities masks - describing high to low level caps
		ptrs - different output driver routines
		ptrs - to various gadgets for device dependant configuration
		ptrs and lengths - of various device dependant configuration
			data structures which may be saved to disk
			for stored setups and defaults


